---
description: Language policy for agent-facing documentation
alwaysApply: true
---

# Agent-facing docs are English

Write documentation that agents read repeatedly — `README.md`, `AGENTS.md`,
`docs/agent-map.md`, `architecture.md`, `docs/canons/**`, group specs, `.cursor/**`
— in **English**, from the start. It is cached every session; one language keeps
the cache tight and cheap.

Russian stays fine for human-tier files (`CHANGELOG.md`, operator runbook) and
product UI strings under `src/`.
